#: djp_sepa/forms.py:32
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"By signing this mandate form, you authorise (A) {provider.creditor} with "
"creditor identifier {provider.creditor_identifier} to send instructions to "
"your bank to debit your account and (B) your bank to debit your account in "
"accordance with the instructions from {provider.creditor}. As part of your "
"rights, you are entitled to a refund from your bank under the terms and "
"conditions of your agreement with your bank. A refund must be claimed within "
"8 weeks starting from the date on which your account was debited."
msgstr ""
"Mit dem Unterzeichnen dieses Mandatsformulars authorisieren Sie (A) "
"{provider.creditor} mit Gläubiger-ID {provider.creditor_identifier}, Ihre "
"Bank zu beauftragen, Ihr Konto zu belasten und (B) Ihre Bank dazu, Ihr Konto "
"entsprechend der Anweisung von {provider.creditor} zu belasten. Sie haben "
"das Recht, die Zahlung entsprechend der Geschäftsbedingungen Ihre Bank "
"zurückzuziehen. Eine Rückgabe muss innerhalb von 8 Wochen nach Belastung "
"Ihres Kontos erfolgen."

